<subSubSection id="E7236CCBEE25DFACD9CE72AA218224C3" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" type="notes">
<paragraph id="85702F70A56DC70FECFF4E395054C352" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="53CAD2FEE340A9937A940F62E4DB581C" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">
Three gatherings were cited in the protologue of 
<taxonomicName id="97ABD2B295E0A03D338C69E61F8EBD3B" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Barthea" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Barthea cavaleriei" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cavaleriei">
<emphasis id="6F3E529F562B64FDA325DDBFCDD0D906" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">Barthea cavaleriei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, viz. Cavalerie 1552, Esquirol 1581 and Esquirol 215, without designation of a type. Two of the syntypes, Esquirol 1581 and 215 were later cited as the types of 
<taxonomicName id="638E433D641AF87F8E2670B2EED20216" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Barthea" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Barthea esquirolii" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="esquirolii">
<emphasis id="16D7A92C9C7A6CFFB615AC4AD0E2DAEB" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">Barthea esquirolii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
H. 
<normalizedToken id="E2E87334984213386EE593145DCF5944" originalValue="Lév">Lev</normalizedToken>
. (1913) and 
<taxonomicName id="5421552FF893E7B6FA31A07EA0778014" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Barthea" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Barthea blinii" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="blinii">
<emphasis id="89B399D36A9B24981CDD0EBD8735C5B9" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">Barthea blinii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
H. 
<normalizedToken id="A5CCC3DCD3EA78C7DD4DC72385B1659C" originalValue="Lév">Lev</normalizedToken>
. (1913), respectively. 
<bibRefCitation id="CC4600045704E6A99CD2B103EE241E77" author="Guillaumin, A" editor="Lecomte, MH" journalOrPublisher="2. G. Masson, Paris" pageId="19" pageNumber="140" pagination="864 - 936" refId="B10" refString="Guillaumin, A, 1913. Melastomataceae. In: Lecomte, MH, Gagnepain, F, Eds., Flore Generale de l'Indo-Chine. 2. G. Masson, Paris: 864 - 936" title="Melastomataceae." volumeTitle="Flore Generale de l'Indo-Chine." year="1913">Guillaumin (1913)</bibRefCitation>
transferred 
<taxonomicName id="1EAAE8BA5D20261D26D844A944CB5153" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Barthea" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Barthea cavaleriei" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cavaleriei">
<emphasis id="058A186D17D24B5EEA3C134904123812" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">Barthea cavaleriei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to 
<taxonomicName id="AEE7264EEA5F348C167ED06F8F2D9F2A" authorityName="Stapf" authorityYear="1892" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Fordiophyton" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Fordiophyton" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="CC05DD44E466DA6FC01552DEC8EAC250" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">Fordiophyton</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
citing only Cavalerie 1552 under the new combination 
<taxonomicName id="191F3BA7582560989A010815DF35B1B0" genus="F." lsidName="F. cavaleriei" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" rank="species" species="cavaleriei">
<emphasis id="6B7804EF1662B044106591F3436BD3FB" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">F. cavaleriei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(H. 
<normalizedToken id="0837785A20C37F912E8E02EB3DF6F750" originalValue="Lév">Lev</normalizedToken>
.) Guillaumin. 
<bibRefCitation id="69D02A7383DA29DDD944B369A0585AA8" author="Diels, L" journalOrPublisher="Botanische Jahrbuecher fuer Systematik, Pflanzengeschichte und Pflanzengeographie" pageId="19" pageNumber="140" pagination="97 - 119" refId="B8" refString="Diels, L, 1932. Beitraege zur Kenntnis der Melastomataceen Ostasiens. Botanische Jahrbuecher fuer Systematik, Pflanzengeschichte und Pflanzengeographie 65: 97 - 119" title="Beitraege zur Kenntnis der Melastomataceen Ostasiens." volume="65" year="1932">Diels (1932)</bibRefCitation>
formally designated Cavalerie 1552 as the lectotype and published a new combination 
<taxonomicName id="700291CA2CDF8153A066AAB63E5977EB" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Bredia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Bredia cavaleriei" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cavaleriei">
<emphasis id="20FB5A6BFD6D39806003EA15195636F3" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">Bredia cavaleriei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(H. 
<normalizedToken id="9305C9227F56065147760E8EF5BB3E17" originalValue="Lév">Lev</normalizedToken>
.) Diels. However, this name is an illegitimate later homonym of 
<taxonomicName id="8433300AE61B0C85C2FBFFC98C28AD3F" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="B." higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. cavaleriei" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cavaleriei">
<emphasis id="BF8C768EE8610C0C1119ED910D2203FF" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">B. cavaleriei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
H. 
<normalizedToken id="BD5055EEFF74A46AD21AA7C5B8DCAB51" originalValue="Lév">Lev</normalizedToken>
. &amp; Vaniot (see Art. 53.1). 
<bibRefCitation id="9DDBAA6FF02DC595507AB409351B6F17" author="Chen, C" editor="Wu, ZY" journalOrPublisher="2. Science Press, Beijing" pageId="19" pageNumber="140" pagination="77 - 137" refId="B2" refString="Chen, C, 1979. Melastomataceae. In: Wu, ZY, Ed., Flora Yunnanica, vol. 2. Science Press, Beijing: 77 - 137" title="Melastomataceae." volumeTitle="Flora Yunnanica, vol." year="1979">Chen (1979)</bibRefCitation>
published the replacement name 
<taxonomicName id="14A98D48E93DA86FD6E4B3ADD159A5AD" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="B." higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. longiradiosa" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="longiradiosa">
<emphasis id="B785FC0BA161ED78309840BA319F0BF9" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">B. longiradiosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
C. Chen for this species, but he did not provide a full reference of the basionym, which makes the name invalid (see Art. 41.1). 
<bibRefCitation id="43387C9F15A6CA7183E4C2FDF15CA0EB" author="Chen, C" journalOrPublisher="Science Press, Beijing," pageId="19" pageNumber="140" pagination="135 - 293" refId="B4" refString="Chen, C, 1984b. Melastomataceae. Flora Reipublicae Popularis Sinicae. Science Press, Beijing, 53: 135 - 293" title="Melastomataceae. Flora Reipublicae Popularis Sinicae." volume="53" year="1984 b">Chen (1984b)</bibRefCitation>
subsequently transferred the species to 
<taxonomicName id="D7E0E49A005F41CBF2BD92A4DD88C2D1" authorityName="Blume" authorityYear="1831" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Phyllagathis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Phyllagathis" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="D609DB24A38356389CE0F37A1B9F7C2D" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">Phyllagathis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. As the epithet 
<emphasis id="4372284C5FBB777EFB8D95219F819E95" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">cavaleriei</emphasis>
is also not available in 
<taxonomicName id="02A2EB4BAC42890AC09AD213F59BCED4" authorityName="Blume" authorityYear="1831" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Phyllagathis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Phyllagathis" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="6EE17E61A502810A322DFF9AE28E5E64" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">Phyllagathis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, a new name 
<taxonomicName id="4755055C1E573380BD2BCE7472E54382" genus="P." lsidName="P. longiradiosa" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" rank="species" species="longiradiosa">
<emphasis id="6C7B3C90CB8301B69790FE14D2EB906B" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">P. longiradiosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
C. Chen was published together with the description of a new variety, 
<taxonomicName id="0000D51CDD3BFA7A76733C60D678CE12" genus="P." infraspecific-rank="var." lsidName="P. longiradiosa var. pulchella" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" rank="variety" species="longiradiosa" variety="pulchella">P. longiradiosa var. pulchella</taxonomicName>
C. Chen. There are three effectively published names for this species in 
<taxonomicName id="1A5D62C0F3D6439AC879AF31FCCB3856" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Bredia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Bredia" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="BC61CD51437B0285F2445C569F991D82" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">Bredia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. With 
<taxonomicName id="DDBE361EE4C9AEC91567044D960474CC" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="B." higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. cavaleriei" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cavaleriei">
<emphasis id="AF98A45C14A19616FF2A44C564EFFBD5" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">B. cavaleriei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(H. 
<normalizedToken id="F37FA427A6E554FC398257717AD8FCE4" originalValue="Lév">Lev</normalizedToken>
.) Diels illegitimate and 
<taxonomicName id="12C5E0CBDB69789DBACD9F5FCC725A50" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="B." higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. longiradiosa" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="longiradiosa">
<emphasis id="3133BABE2FBD165E46039B4404D12571" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">B. longiradiosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
C. Chen invalid, the only legitimate name, 
<taxonomicName id="D79A924EC3BD489A049D3B9597AF8CC4" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="B." higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. longiradiosa" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="longiradiosa">
<emphasis id="92D80343AE23169084471E6D4147B45B" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">B. longiradiosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
C. Chen ex Govaerts is adopted as the correct name for this species.
</paragraph>
